      <h2 class="section-title">What does<br><em>Tesserae</em> mean?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--charcoal-mid); margin-bottom:1.5rem; text-align:justify; hyphens:auto;">In Latin lies our origin: <strong>Tesserae</strong>, the pieces that together form a masterpiece. From Rome, this name has meant <em>"pact"</em> and <em>"alliance."</em> Tesserae is our identity.</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--charcoal-mid); margin-bottom:1.5rem; text-align:justify; hyphens:auto;">For us, Law is the tool and the mosaic is the path. We unite every detail of your case with technical precision to build a solid and complete legal strategy.</p>
      <p style="font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); line-height:1.6;">"Tesserae implies the pact between ourselves and our commitment to our clients."</p>
